      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been maintained to the most exacting standards, exhibiting a showroom-quality finish and a mechanical profile that mirrors its original factory specifications. Every surface, from the hand-finished interior to the flawless exterior paintwork, reflects a legacy of meticulous preservation. We invite discerning collectors and enthusiasts to experience this benchmark of excellence firsthand.",
