    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s been pampered since day one and is in truly spectacular condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Everything is crisp, clean, and ready for a new home. If you've been looking for a ride that\u2019s been treated with nothing but love, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
