    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L high-compression inline-six. This unit boasts a flawlessly synchronized dual-VANOS system and six individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. Power is delivered via a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a 3.62:1 limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including documented rear subframe reinforcement and a recent shim-and-bucket valve clearance adjustment. The chassis is laser-straight, retaining its factory kinematic balance with original Sachs dampers and refreshed bushings. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior exhibits zero clear coat failure or oxidation. A true turn-key performance icon with no mechanical lash or fluid leaks.",
